title: Do You Code Switch (Talk White)

description:
Wednesday 6/20 - Today on the show we had the cast of "Sorry To Bother You" stop by where they discussed the meaning of the movie, Terry Crews discussed his sexual allegation case, and "The Breakfast Club" couldn't differentiate Omari Hardwick and his role Ghost during the interview. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a North Charleston man who tried to speed off from cops, but his car was in park ( womp womp). Also, Angela Yee helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee" and one listener was trying to scoop her a baller.
